    "description": {
      "value": "<h2>Standard Racial Traits</h2><ul><li><b>Ability Scores:</b> +2 <em>Constitution</em>, +2 <em>Intelligence</em>, –2 <em>Wisdom</em>.</li><li><b>Size:</b> Yaddithians are Medium creatures and thus receive no bonuses or penalties due to their size.</li><li><b>Type:</b> Yaddithians are Aberrations.</li><li><b>Speed:</b> Yaddithians have a land speed of 20 feet.</li><li><b>Languages:</b> Yaddithians begin play speaking Yaddithian. Those with high <em>Intelligence</em> scores can choose any language as a bonus language.</li></ul><h3>Senses</h3><ul><li><b>Darkvision:</b> Yaddithians can see in the dark up to 60 feet.</li></ul><h3>Offensive Racial Traits</h3><ul><li><b>Claws:</b> A Yaddithian has two claws that deal 1d4 points of damage each.</li></ul><h3>Defensive Racial Traits</h3><ul><li><b>Defensive Abilities:</b> Yaddithians have cold <em>resistance</em> 5 and the <em>no breath</em> ability.</li><li><b>Rugose:</b> A Yaddithian gains a +1 <em>natural armor bonus</em>.</li></ul><h3>Other Racial Traits</h3><ul><li><b>Cosmic Mind (Ex)</b>: A Yaddithian gets a +2 <em>racial bonus</em> on <em>Knowledge</em> and <em>Spellcraft</em> checks. A yaddithian spellcaster who would store spells in a <em>spellbook</em> or <em>familiar</em> instead stores those spells in its mind (but must expend the normal resources to learn new spells).</li><li><b>Long-Lived (Ex)</b>: Yaddithians live for thousands of years; they gain no benefit or penalty from aging and are immune to magical aging effects.</li></ul>"
    },
